I"<p>This is cool, but <a href="http://www.rogueamoeba.com/audiohijackpro/">Audio Hijack Pro</a> (which I like so much I recently bought it) is still too hard too use for podcasting. <a href="http://www.ambrosiasw.com/utilities/wiretap/">WireTap Pro</a> is cheaper and much easier to use and will probably do the job for most Mac podcasters.</p>
